      "content": "makes sense. so basically even if someone thinks certain content is \"bad\" or \"dangerous,\" the philosophical stance is that the government's intervention is still illegitimate because it violates that autonomy? it's hard to see how the \"harm\" argument would ever justify regulations in that framework then.",
